Comment: Not only have I so far mentioned the monsters that would appear in Hotel Transylvania 2. I also have so far mentioned new monsters that Hotel Transylvania 2 would feature. All the new monsters but the Boogie Man and Merlin, which I mentioned in my comments so far, are not the only new monsters it featured. The film featured a number of other new monsters like the Invisible Man's girlfriend. The new monsters that Hotel Transylvania 2 featured did not include Godzilla or El Chupacabra. Godzilla & El Chupacabra had a slight chance of appearing in there but they didn't appear in there. No, they did not. I had hoped they would not forget to add Igor, Medusa, the Swamp Thing, King Kong, the Creature from the Black Lagoon, and the Phantom of the Opera, but the Phantom of the Opera was the only new monster out of those 6 monsters that appeared in the movie. So, unlike him, the other 5 did not appear.

Because he never recovered from being frozen by Dracula in the first movie and because Dracula fired him. Opposed to appearing in the film, Martha was mentioned.
